itable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2004)\n! scope=\"col\"| Position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| UK Albums (OCC)<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/end-of-year-artist-albums-chart/20040104/37502/ |title=End of Year Album Chart Top 100 \u2013 2004 |publisher=Official Charts Company |date=January 8, 2005 |accessdate=September 22, 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401163703/https://www.officialcharts.com/charts/end-of-year-artist-albums-chart/20040104/37502/ |archive-date=April 1, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n| 34\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US ''Billboard'' 200<ref name=\"Billboard 200\">{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/276709/kanye-west/chart?f=412 |title=Kanye West \u2013 Chart history |work=Billboard |accessdate=July 8, 2014 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150309132705/http://www.billboard.com/artist/276709/kanye-west/chart?f=412 |archivedate=March 9, 2015  }}</ref>\n| 12\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US Top R&B/Hip-Hop Albums (''Billboard'')<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2004/top-r-b-hip-hop-albums|title=2004 Year-End Charts \u2013 Billboard R&B/Hip-Hop Albums|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|accessdate=February 28, 2015|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141205073014/http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2004/top-r-b-hip-hop-albums|archivedate=December 5, 2014}}</ref>\n| 4\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Worldwide Charts ([[International Federation of the Phonographic Industry|IFPI]])<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20110410040332/https://www.musikindustrie.de/uploads/media/top50-2004.pdf \"Top 50 Global Best Selling Albums for 2004\"] (PDF). [[International Federation of the Phonographic Industry|IFPI]]. Archived from [https://www.musikindustrie.de/uploads/media/top50-2004.pdf the original] on April 10, 2011. Retrieved December 7, 2019.</ref>\n| 21\n|}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable pl